
Competencies

Up until now we’ve been creating our database by hand
Active Record is an ORM (Object Relational Mapping) implementation for Rails
Connects relational database tables to our ruby applications
Uses Ruby’s robust class relationships to integrate databases into applications
Inheritance, validations, other relationships all translate over via Active Record

Applications
Implement Active Record in applications
Understand the inherent Ruby Class integration

Active Record documentation:

https://github.com/rails/rails/tree/master/activerecord


Active Record Rails Guide: 

http://guides.rubyonrails.org/active_record_basics.html
